<div style="background-color:white;padding:10px"><h3>About us</h3></div>
<div style="background-color:white;padding:10px">
<p>GreenCoinX is an open source software program developed to provide digital identification crypto currency. Nilam Doctor, the lead developer, teamed up with Canadian public company <a href="http://www.greenbankcapitalinc.com/" target="_blank">GreenBank Capital Inc</a> (CSE:GBC) to form GreenCoin Inc a software company focused on creating a cryptocurrency that has the potential for widespread adoption.  The result is XGC, a unique cryptocurrency that identifies users and enables governments to collect transaction taxes.</p>
<p>Through development additional features were developed that include the abilities to send funds to others via their email or mobile number, and to add optional additional information, allowing for a much friendly customer interaction by bypassing the need for the standard long code bitcoin address.</p>
<p>The result is XGC, a unique Cryptocurrency that can identify users whilst providing an easier sender/receiver capabilities and enables governments to collect transaction taxes when relevant. </p>

<p>Nilam Doctor is the lead developer of GreenCoinX and a technology consultant and programmer. He has provided technical services in Cryptourrency projects, and provided technical services in crypto currency related projects for development, security, and applications. He is a graduate of Gujarat University with an MBA in Finance and a Bachelor of Engineering.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.greenbankcapitalinc.com/" target="_blank">GreenBank Capital Inc</a> is a corporate finance investment company listed on the Canadian Securities Exchange (symbol GBC). For more information on GreenBank please see <a href="http://www.greenbankcapitalinc.com/" target="_blank">www.GreenBankCapitalinc.com</a> </p>
